SYNOPSIS: Adapted from The Bacchae, <b><i>Aves + Autta + Ino + Mel</i></b> by Rebecca Ana Peña centers the lives and sisterhood of Agave, Autonoë, Ino, and Semele as they navigate a world of gods, violence, and Bacchic frenzy. Dedicated to changing their fate, they steadfastly create the world they dream about; however, everything’s not always what it seems.
<div>DATE + TIME: 4/28/25, 7pm ET, Playwrights Downtown's Studio 3G, 440 Lafayette, NYC</div>
